Linux --> ssh / port 22
windows --> RDP / port 3389

authentication / authorization --> key pair

AWS Network
Region --> VPC (Virtual Private Cloud)
AZs --> Subnets ( every AZ has a unique subnet)

Connect to linux server using ssh command from windows command prompt:
ssh -i "aws-oct-key-2024.pem" ubuntu@13.201.88.221

ubuntu --> debian -- apt
amazon linux, redhat --> centos --> yum


